                    <msContents>
                        <summary><title type="uniform">Heimskringla</title>.<note>The manuscript
                                contains fragments of <title type="uniform">Heimskringla</title>.
                                The contents are similar to <title>Kringla</title>, but several
                                parts are omitted, not only in <title type="uniform">Ólafs saga
                                    helga</title>, but also in <title>Sigurðar saga
                                    Jórsalafara</title> , <title>Magnússona saga</title> and
                                    <title>Magnús saga blinda</title>.</note></summary>
