                        <decoDesc>
                            <decoNote type="initial">
                                <p> The major initials on fol. <locus>12r</locus> (the beginning of
                                        <title type="uniform">Magnús saga góða</title> ) and on fol.
                                        <locus>18v</locus> are <foreign xml:lang="la">litterae
                                        florissae</foreign> with branches and leaves. </p>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote type="initial">
                                <p>The black pen-flourished majuscules that open each chapter fill
                                    two or three lines. They seems to be younger than the text and
                                    many of them are extended in the margin.</p>
                            </decoNote>
                        </decoDesc>
                        <additions>
                            <p> At the bottom of fol. <locus>7v</locus>
                                <name type="person" key="ArnMag001">Árni Magnússon</name> has
                                written: <q xml:lang="is"> þetta blad kom til mïn ur Middlum
