                                </q> , and at the bottom of fol. <locus>9r</locus> he has written:
                                    <q xml:lang="is"> Utan af qvere fra <name type="person"
                                        key="SigErl001">Sigride Erlendzdottur</name> Olafs sonar p
                                        <expan>rests</expan> ad <name type="place">Melstad</name>
                                </q>
                            </p>
                        </additions>
